com.bitplan.expr

Interface NumexprListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NumexprBaseListener

    public interface NumexprListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by NumexprParser.
